{"tid":570421,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"Vocal guitar 想組隊原創band (有demo)","createTime":"2018-02-23T15:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T11:27:06.000Z","uid":33904,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54f8afddf9062cdb93bdd0bedca0b942fd6432ee","tid":570421,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T15:35:45.000Z","msg":"主要聽開：<br />\n<br />\nポルカドットスティングレイ<br />\n東京事變<br />\nおいしくるメロンパン<br />\n<br />\n識 d cubase 錄音 編曲 mixing，<br />\n可以用guitar pro 打完譜再入midi加其他樂器，<br />\n少少 Lead guitar，<br />\n強項係砌chord progression (算係花巧少少既野)、作vocal melody 同main riffs。<br />\n<br />\n想要個玩cutting勁, blues, funk, jazz都識d 既 lead guitar，<br />\n最好其中一個member填詞勁，<br />\n因為自己算係好快作到野出黎，<br />\n但係填詞拖十世既人，如果有人幫手填詞既話可以好快就作到一首出黎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既留個tg我sd demo比你地"},{"pid":"3b2f9c4619022e6574fe262b57173488ed60389a","tid":570421,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"推一野"},{"pid":"43b76b6d34a08ff16e98f82c3993dacdd7061e68","tid":570421,"uid":7193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆你應該搵個好groove既bass先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8d201de55b9e5a74f503114d9f36b05f5e1ea9","tid":570421,"uid":3615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"ポルカ正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我結他好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0950b9a7afa2257e0fef9c056711532ed10a5c36","tid":570421,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b76b6d34a08ff16e98f82c3993dacdd7061e68","tid":570421,"uid":7193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆你應該搵個好groove既bass先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T19:31:28.000Z","msg":"問題係有冇先<img src=\"/assets/face